dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours, shading and spot heights. In upper margin: Ordnance survey of England and Wales. Sheet 24. "Reduced from the one inch map of 1904-07. Published at the Ordnance Survey Office, Southampton in 1915 by Colonel C.F. Close C.M.G., R.E., Director General."--In margin below map. Originally issued folded in covers 18 x 10 cm.
